<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ز ر م:</span> <span class="c2">(زَرِمَ)</span> الْبَوْلُ بِالْكَسْرِ انْقَطَعَ وَ <span class="c2">(أَزْرَمَهُ)</span> غَيْرُهُ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا تُزْرِمُوهُ»</span> أَيْ لَا تَقْطَعُوا عَلَيْهِ بَوْلَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>